    "description": {
      "value": "<p>If hit, the target loses its next turn. In addition, it loses its Dexterity bonus to Defense for the next attack made against it. Your next attack or technique must have the target as its (primary) target. If that technique is a<br><br>Taijutsu technique, you automatically succeed at the Perform check. If the subject dies or you become unable to reach it with your next attack or technique, you lose your next turn. If the follow-up attack is made in the same round as this technique, the target does not lose its next turn. You are considered @Condition[flatFooted]{flat-footed} until your next action.<br><br>A target cannot be affected by this technique more than once every 3 rounds.</p>\n\n\n\n",
